Accepted: January 2003
Interpretation of heart rate variability via detrended fluctuation analysis and αβ filter
Chaos 13 , 467 (2003); https://doi.org/10.1063/1.1562051
J. C. Echeverrı́a
School of Electrical and Electronic Engineering, University of Nottingham, Nottingham, United Kingdom
Electrical Engineering Department, Universidad Autónoma Metropolitana-Izt., México City, México
M. S. Woolfson , J. A. Crowe , and B. R. Hayes-Gill
School of Electrical and Electronic Engineering, University of Nottingham, Nottingham, United Kingdom
G. D. H. Croaker
Nottingham City Hospital, Nottingham, United Kingdom
Queens Medical Centre, Nottingham, United Kingdom
H. Vyas
Queens Medical Centre, Nottingham, United Kingdom
